Han Seung Jae.

557
00:38:15,430 --> 00:38:16,430
Yes, ma'am.

558
00:38:19,470 --> 00:38:20,540
Wipe your face with this.

559
00:38:47,900 --> 00:38:48,930
What are you doing?

560
00:38:51,270 --> 00:38:52,540
