I finished checking
the volunteer activities.

625
00:44:37,410 --> 00:44:38,450
- Really?
- Yes.

626
00:44:39,410 --> 00:44:40,520
I must've fallen asleep.

627
00:44:45,250 --> 00:44:48,120
(BM Edu-City:
Promotional news and articles)

628
00:44:48,120 --> 00:44:51,060
