766
00:52:17,870 --> 00:52:18,910
I'll pass as well.

767
00:52:19,070 --> 00:52:20,780
She's scary, so same here.

768
00:52:21,240 --> 00:52:22,280
Same here.

769
00:52:24,510 --> 00:52:25,550
Hae Seong, where are you going?

770
00:52:28,420 --> 00:52:30,390
